{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Car insurance annual premiums should not cost more than the vehicle value",
        "additional_details": "This is because insurance premiums for newer drivers can often exceed the price of the vehicle they are driving, making it unaffordable for many drivers.",
        "background": "I would like for Parliament to introduce legislation enforced by the FCA (Financial Conduct Authority) to cap car annual insurance premiums at the value of the vehicle for car insurance companies.",
